Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个月也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下个月再努力吧\N(南条亚美菜)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉这样永远不会怀孕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,(羞耻的无法怀孕治疗)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(沉迷受孕精油按摩的人妻)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对怀孕好的按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我在网上查了一下这个按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,评价很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去试试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想早点见到小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能做什麽都试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,上次怀孕是什麽时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,1年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有怀孕的原因是荷尔蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的按摩会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我保管衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请趴在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先涂精油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有过敏的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不会很痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从後背开始按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会太用力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量放松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,脊椎有点弯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,手臂直着放下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,直着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,比刚才更用力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,身体哪里容易僵硬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,肩膀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,左边的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有点肿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是下半身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请放松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要刺激淋巴 所以更用力点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,淋巴都塞住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,身体舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,头有点晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是荷尔蒙扩散了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请正面朝上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,伸直身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把腿伸展到和肩膀一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请放松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我加精油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伸直腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和肩膀同宽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刺激淋巴了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,用力的话效果就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量放松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都是积累的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,按下半身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,张开腿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,身体变热了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好热哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可能很符合本店的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伸直的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,按摩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要拉伸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最近感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没有哦\N是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,淋巴怎麽会塞住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,伸直腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起来有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽样啊按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很微妙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我在网上看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,据说什麽样的女性去了都会怀孕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还是继续去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再多试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我们的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为了未来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的急事赶上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,比之前好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,腿部放松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要按这里的骨头 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,神经都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,比上次脊柱更直了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想再做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,正面朝上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把身体伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吐气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吐气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,吐气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再拉伸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,身体伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量伸直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要让荷尔蒙活跃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,来我们店不就是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是来按摩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢按摩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那乳头还硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,自己很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,最近乳头硬过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,按摩很有效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想怀孕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要忍耐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.89,0:24:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,直接涂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.41,0:24:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.71,0:24:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很有效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.04,0:25:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.66,0:26:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,转身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.26,0:26:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.15,0:26:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.87,0:26:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想怀孕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.14,0:27:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,按摩更有效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很热哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.99,0:27:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.43,0:27:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.63,0:28:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.07,0:28:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.12,0:28:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.83,0:28:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.33,0:29:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样按不到穴位
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.23,0:29:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,张开腿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.96,0:29:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可能会怀孕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.79,0:29:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样更有效哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.73,0:29:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.89,0:29:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再久一点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.23,0:29:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会怀孕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.27,0:29:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.23,0:30:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.34,0:30:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.87,0:30:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,按你喜欢的做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.11,0:30:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要介意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.86,0:30:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.87,0:32:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.33,0:33:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒很大能都进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.27,0:33:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舔舔
