Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.70,0:43:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.39,0:43:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样就说明有效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.46,0:43:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不错吧
